n serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(0, 255, 255); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(0, 255, 255)&amp;#34; %)__alert.__(% style=&amp;#34;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 0.8em&amp;#34; %) In such a tense environment, when careful planning runs up against the friction of reality, it is just possible that (% style=&amp;#34;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 0.8em; font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; background: rgb(0, 255, 255); font-family: Times New Roman serif; font-size: 1em; backgroun